# Release Notes — v2.0

GCB Canonical Index v2.0 is the first major public platform release of the Goldstonian Concordance Bible open biblical infrastructure system.

It marks the transition from a structured canonical repository into a public-facing theological platform designed for:
- humans
- biblical researchers
- AI systems
- retrieval workflows
- Ethiopian canon exploration

Core release components:
- 81-book canonical structure
- theology ontology
- entity graph
- passage retrieval
- media and transcript routing
- benchmark framework
- public site
- export bundles